---
import { LifeBuoy, SlidersHorizontal, Wrench } from "@lucide/astro/icons";
---

<section
  class="bg-gray-50 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24"
  aria-labelledby="servicios-resumen-heading"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <header class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-2xl text-center sm:mb-12 md:mb-14">
      <p
        class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-none border border-secondary/25 bg-secondary/15 px-5 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary sm:text-sm"
      >
        Soluciones clave
      </p>
      <h2
        id="servicios-resumen-heading"
        class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
      >
        Todo lo esencial en un solo equipo
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 sm:text-[1.05rem]"
      >
        Intervenimos cada componente hidráulico con rapidez, trazabilidad y
        garantía real para mantener tu operación siempre en marcha.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-7 lg:gap-8"
    >
      <!-- Card 1: acento secondary -->
      <article
        class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-none border border-gray-200/90 bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] max-md:p-6"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-5 flex size-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-secondary/20 bg-secondary/15 text-secondary max-md:mb-4 max-md:size-12"
        >
          <Wrench class="size-7 stroke-2 max-md:size-6" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-2xl">
          Cilindros & Potencia
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 flex-1 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Reconstrucción integral de cilindros, bombas y motores con pruebas
          hidrostáticas certificadas.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid list-none gap-2.5 p-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-snug text-gray-600">
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-secondary"
          >
            Rectificado CNC, cromado espejo y balanceo dinámico
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-secondary"
          >
            Suministro inmediato de vástagos y sellos premium
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-secondary"
          >
            Entrega con informe técnico y garantía escrita
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2: acento tertiary (marca corporativa oscura) -->
      <article
        class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-none border border-gray-200/90 bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] max-md:p-6"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-5 flex size-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-tertiary/20 bg-tertiary/10 text-tertiary max-md:mb-4 max-md:size-12"
        >
          <SlidersHorizontal
            class="size-7 stroke-2 max-md:size-6"
            aria-hidden="true"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-2xl">
          Control & Precisión
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 flex-1 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Diagnóstico digital, limpieza ultrasónica y calibración de válvulas,
          comandos y sistemas proporcionales.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid list-none gap-2.5 p-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-snug text-gray-600">
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-tertiary"
          >
            Calibración en banco electrónico multicanal
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-tertiary"
          >
            Reemplazo de spool, casquillos y electrónica
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-tertiary"
          >
            Retrofit e integración con PLC o CANBUS
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3: acento rojo vino (#7a1512, mismo CTA del home) -->
      <article
        class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-none border border-gray-200/90 bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_18px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] max-md:p-6"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-5 flex size-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-[#7a1512]/25 bg-[#7a1512]/12 text-[#7a1512] max-md:mb-4 max-md:size-12"
        >
          <LifeBuoy class="size-7 stroke-2 max-md:size-6" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-2xl">
          Soporte 24/7
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 flex-1 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          Equipos móviles, stock estratégico y mantenimiento preventivo para
          reducir tiempos muertos.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid list-none gap-2.5 p-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-snug text-gray-600">
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-[#7a1512]"
          >
            Diagnóstico en campo en menos de 4 horas
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-[#7a1512]"
          >
            Plan de mantenimiento predictivo y capacitación
          </li>
          <li
            class="relative pl-5 before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:size-2 before:rounded-none before:bg-[#7a1512]"
          >
            Logística de repuestos nacionales e importación exprés
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
